{
  "date": "2026-04-03",
  "title": "When It’s Time to Let Go…. What Comes Out?",
  "scriptures": [
    {
      "ref": "John 19:30",
      "text": "It is finished."
    },
    {
      "ref": "Luke 23:46",
      "text": "Father, into Your hands I commit My spirit."
    }
  ],
  "sections": [
    {
      "key": "moment_on_the_cross",
      "label": "Moment on the Cross",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Your body is at its limit.",
            "Every breath is slower now.",
            "There’s nothing left to prove.",
            "Nothing left to do."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "Will you trust…. or will you hold on?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "read_this_out_loud",
      "label": "Read This Out Loud",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Most men don’t struggle with effort….",
            "They struggle with surrender."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "devotional",
      "label": "Devotional",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Jesus doesn’t say:",
            "“I hope I did enough.”",
            "He says:",
            "👉 Finished."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "The work is complete.",
            "The debt is paid.",
            "The mission is fulfilled."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "And then",
            "👉 He releases everything.",
            "“Into Your hands….”"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bullet_list",
          "items": [
            "Keep striving",
            "Keep proving",
            "Keep controlling"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Because letting go feels like losing.",
            "But Jesus shows us:",
            "👉 Letting go is trust."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "reflex_test",
      "label": "Reflex Test",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "bullet_list",
          "items": [
            "Out of control",
            "Uncertain about outcomes",
            "Pressure to prove something"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "👉 Do you tighten…. or trust?"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "the_90_second_window",
      "label": "The 90-Second Window",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "In moments of pressure:"
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Pause.",
            "Because what you choose in seconds shapes who you become for years."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "shadow_confession",
      "label": "Shadow Confession",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "I try to control more than I trust."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "gem",
      "label": "Gem",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "quote",
          "text": "You will never experience peace while trying to control what God already holds."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "good_friday_moment",
      "label": "Good Friday Moment (Don’t Rush This)",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Father, forgive them….",
            "Today you will be with me….",
            "Behold your son….",
            "My God, why have You forsaken Me….",
            "I thirst….",
            "It is finished….",
            "Into Your hands…."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "👉 Every word spoken under pressure",
            "👉 Every response aligned",
            "👉 Every moment surrendered"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "What would come out of me…. if I were on that cross?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "which_man_are_you_becoming",
      "label": "Which Man Are You Becoming?",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "bullet_list",
          "items": [
            "The Reactor (emotion-led)",
            "The Avoider (comfort-led)",
            "The Performer (approval-led)",
            "The Controller (fear-led)",
            "The Surrendered Man (Spirit-led)"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "invitation",
      "label": "1 Invitation",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "bullet_list",
          "items": [
            "Control",
            "Fear",
            "Pressure",
            "Identity",
            "Outcome"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "Father…. into Your hands…."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "final_line",
      "label": "Final Line",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "You are not preparing for a future moment….",
            "👉 You are rehearsing for it right now.",
            "And the cross doesn’t just show you what Jesus did….",
            "👉 It reveals what’s still being formed in you."
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "__insert_block_header": "2026-04-03_john-19-30_when-its-time-to-let-go-what-comes-out|"
}
